product.name: Nike Air Force 1 '07
product.description: The radiance lives on in the Nike Air Force 1 '07, the b-ball OG that puts a fresh spin on what you know best: crisp leather, clean colourways and the perfect amount of flash to make you shine. This clean, pure white finish adds the gum-sole contrast for a fresh, versatile look with just the right amount of pop.
